王叢桂。(1992)。大學生校園適應、求助意願與潛在求助者間關係的探討。「大專心理衛生」研討會。臺北：教育部訓委會主辦。
Wang, C. K.。(2004)。An investigation on factors moderate feelings of trust between Taiwan managers and their subordinate workers in China。XⅦth International Congress International Association for Cross-Cultural Psychology。陜西師範大學 西安 中國大陸。
Wang, C. K.。(2002)。The construction of parenthood and its consequences on Taiwanese work values.。XXV International Congress of Applied Psychology at National University of Singapore。Singapore。
Wang, C. K.。(2001)。The Transmission of Work Values Between College-Graduated Workers and Their Parents.。Asian Social Psychology in the 21st Century at The University of Melbourne。The University of Melbourne, Victoria, Australia。
Wang, C. K.。(1999)。Fatherhood, Motherhood and Career Commitment.。Conference of Asian Association of Social Psychology。Taipei。
Wang, C. K.。(1999)。Fatherhood Schema and its Relationship with Sex Role Beliefs,Work Values of Taiwanese Students.。Convention ofInternational Council of Psychologist。Salem, MA., U.S.A.。


